1) Touchpad behavior

   Precision TouchPad compatible device (buttonless, multi‑touch) .
   Support comes from CONFIG_INPUT_TOUCHPAD, HID Multitouch, and i2c‑hid — these allow libinput (in Xorg) to detect and use gestures.

  There are no special proprietary drivers needed. If cleanliness or responsiveness is lacking, configure libinput behavior in Xorg or desktop environment.
