2) Recommended GRUB kernel parameters

  In /etc/default/grub: intel_iommu=igfx_off nvidia-drm.modeset=1
      Explanation:
      intel_iommu=igfx_off reduces possible ACPI/IOMMU issues with Comet Lake hardware.
      nvidia-drm.modeset=1 enables KMS for NVIDIA PRIME offload. 
  
  Regenerate config: grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg

